library(viridis)

ggplot(data=storms)+
  geom_jitter(aes(x= as.factor(month), y = pressure, fill=wind), pch= 21, alpha=.05)+
  scale_fill_viridis_c()+
  theme_bw()+
  labs(title= "Hurrican Pressure V Month", subtitle = "with Max Wind Speed", X = "Month")
